{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_0_level_main_00-02_beg","storyGroup":"main_0","storySort":5,"storyDependence":"main_0_level_main_00-01_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"0-2","storyName":"守卫","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"电视中播放着胜利的喜讯，然而现实中，一切都在预示着切尔诺伯格的毁灭。\n但对小心谨慎的罗德岛来说，他们尚有一线生机——\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_00-02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_00-02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["杜宾","电视主持人","整合运动成员","乌萨斯军警","乌萨斯军警队长","近卫干员","阿米娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第二关（前）","id":0},{"type":"background","id":1},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$escape_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_escape_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":2,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/62/Avg_bg_bg_cher_1.png","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":6},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":7},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"......这终归还是，太超乎我的想象了。","id":8,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"爆炸，骚乱，火光，巷战......","id":9,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"难道整个切尔诺伯格，都陷入了这种混乱吗？","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":12},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_bg_0_tv.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":13},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":14},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"-20","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"在切尔诺伯格军警的团结协作与迅速反应之下......","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"......情况已经被控制，大部分区域的意外事件已经被镇压。","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"目前，切尔诺伯格军警已经包围了盘踞在瓦舒克大道上的暴徒......","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"可见，这一次无谋的袭击，将很快结束。","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"请各位不要惊慌，待在屋中，等待切尔诺伯格的又一场胜利......","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电视主持人","text":"乌萨斯的荣光保佑着陛下和他的人民！","id":21},{"type":"dialog","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":24},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/62/Avg_bg_bg_cher_1.png","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":25},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"......","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警","text":"可恶，他们，他们......那些武器和装备，究竟是哪里来的！","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"不要畏缩！就算穿上护甲，懦夫依旧是懦夫！不过是些缺乏训练的暴徒！","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警","text":"可是，可是他们的数量......！！","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"我们已经干掉了我们数量三倍之多的敌人！再干掉三倍的敌人，战斗就结束了！","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"少口出狂言了，切尔诺伯格的混蛋！","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"感染者渣滓，也配和我们为敌？！","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"逮捕你们和你们肮脏的爹妈时就该把你们全部当场处死，而不是流放和苦役！","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"你们这些家伙......！！","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警","text":"呃......！他们在冲击防线，前卫没法再支撑多长时间了！","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"为了陛下！给我顶住！！","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警","text":"我，我要......坚持不住了......！","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警队长","text":"退后的人，统统处死！","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯军警","text":"咳......","id":46},{"type":"character","id":47},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"dialog","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"character","name":"char_013_riop","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫干员","text":"我们......","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_char_013_riop.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"待在这里别动！我们还不能暴露！","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"乌萨斯的军警队伍......居然被整合运动压制住了？","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_char_002_amiya_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"哼......电视上播放的内容，和现实完全不一样。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"切尔诺伯格当局，到了这个时候，还在耍这种手段吗。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"不过，对于我们来说，事情也同样在变糟。指望通过更加隐秘的手段离开，已经不现实了。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"糟糕的路况和敌人的封锁......我们已经没办法再利用载具分别行动了......","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"char_130_doberm_ex","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"是的，救援小队只有在具备一定规模时，才能有效消灭盘踞在要道上的整合运动敌人。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"再切分小队，只会是自取灭亡。","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_013_riop","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫干员","text":"这些乌萨斯军警......","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_char_013_riop.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫干员","text":"即使他们的装备很精良，看起来也很有实力，但整合运动......","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_char_013_riop.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫干员","text":"无论是人数还是士气，都占压倒性的优势！","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_char_013_riop.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"和我们对切尔诺伯格进行初步侦察时完全不同......","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"在我们潜入时，切尔诺伯格军警与驻扎部队的数量、分布，以及状态，处在一个非常古怪的状态。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"只是在那个时候，我们没办法确定原因而已。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_013_riop","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫干员","text":"难道整合运动，已经秘密地消灭了切尔诺伯格的大部分防卫力量吗？","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_char_013_riop.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"没有任何证据可以证明，整合运动的力量真的庞大到如此地步，还能够谋划这么大规模的战略......","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"现在，我怕是只能庆幸，被包围的是那些军警，而不是我们。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"当然，我们也必须提防四周的情况，等到陷入危机，就已经晚了——","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......博士，快召集各小队。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"侦查干员发现了整合运动，他们马上就要和我们的救援队伍接触了！","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"——至少，我们现在的优势，也就只有谨小慎微这一点了。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"character","id":85},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"dialog","id":87},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"嗯？","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"这，这里也有武装力量？！","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"各小队，作战准备！不要给他们反击的机会！","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_char_130_doberm_ex.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":94},{"type":"dialog","id":95},{"type":"blocker","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"image","id":97}],"characters":["杜宾","电视主持人","整合运动成员","乌萨斯军警","乌萨斯军警队长","近卫干员","阿米娅"]}